                 <p>The Club Penguin Shop uses the following freight methods, as   determined by the total weight of your order, which is calculated prior to   checkout:</p>
<ul>
  <li><strong>  <a href="#standard" class="iconlinks">United States Postal Service - Standard</a></strong></li>
  <li><strong><a href="#ups" class="iconlinks">United Parcel Service (UPS Selected Services)</a></strong><br>
    </li>
  </ul>
<p class="blue_title">&nbsp;</p>
<h2><a name="standard"></a><span class="style1">United States Postal Service - Standard: </span></h2>
<p>USA orders up to 1 pound: <br>
                   United States Postal Service - First Class Mail<br>
                   Please Allow 1 - 2 Weeks for Delivery...Shipping &amp; Handling is less than $10.00 USD </p>
                 <p>USA orders over 1 pound: <br>
                   United States Postal Service - Parcel Post<br>
                   Please Allow 1 - 2 Weeks for Delivery...Shipping &amp; Handling is calculated in Shopping Cart </p>
                 <p>Canadian orders up to 3 pounds: <br>
                   United States Postal Service - Global Priority Mail Canada<br>
                   Please Allow 2 Weeks for Delivery...Shipping &amp; Handling is less than $20.00 USD </p>
                 <p>Canadian orders over 3 pounds: <br>
                   United States Postal Service - Canada Parcel Post Airmail<br>
                   Please Allow 2 - 3 Weeks for Delivery...Shipping &amp; Handling is calculated in Shopping Cart </p>
                 <p>International orders up to 3 pounds: <br>
                   United States Postal Service - Global Priority Mail International<br>
                   Please Allow 3 - 5 Weeks for Delivery...Shipping &amp; Handling is less than $30.00 USD<br>
                   <span class="note">(Service for the United Kingdom, Mexico, Australia, New Zealand, Japan &amp; China) </span></p>
                 <p>International orders over 3 pounds: <br>
                   United States Postal Service - International Parcel Post Airmail<br>
                   Please Allow 4 - 6 Weeks for Delivery...Shipping &amp; Handling is calculated in Shopping Cart</p>
                 <p class="note">For Canadian &amp; International orders - Customs and Duty charges will be applicable upon receipt of your order. </p>
                 <p align="right"><a href="#top"><br>
                  Back to top</a></p>
                 
                 <h2 align="left"><a name="ups"></a><span class="style1">United Parcel Service (UPS Selected Services)</span>:</h2>
                 The details on the selected   UPS services below pertain to the USA only. For Canadian &amp; International   customers wanting to use UPS Worldwide services, please e-mail us with the shop   items you would like to purchase and your complete shipping address with phone   number  at:
                  
                    </span> <script language=javascript><!--
	  var name = "cpshop"
	  var site = "clubpenguin.com"
	  var link = name + "@" + site
	  document.write("<b><a href=" + "mail" + "to:" + link + ">" + link + "</a></b>")
	  //--></script></p>
                 <p><br>
                   UPS 2nd Day Air: USA Service with Tracking Number<br>
  Please Allow 2-4 Business Days for Delivery...Shipping &amp; Handling is calculated in Shopping Cart </p>
                 <p>UPS 3 Day Select: USA Service with Tracking Number<br>
                   Please Allow 3-5 Business Days for Delivery...Shipping &amp; Handling is calculated in Shopping Cart </p>
                 <p>UPS Ground: USA Service with Tracking Number<br>
                   Please Allow 7 Business Days for Delivery...Shipping &amp; Handling is calculated in Shopping Cart</p>
                 <p>
